{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6307c","heading":"Sanctioning organizations","label":"6307c Sanctioning organizations","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch89","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsA prior was renumbered section 19 and is classified to .section 11 of Pub. L. 104–272section 6310 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Objective criteria","label":"a Objective criteria","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Within 2 years after , the Association of Boxing Commissions shall develop and shall approve by a vote of no less than a majority of its member State boxing commissioners, guidelines for objective and consistent written criteria for the ratings of professional boxers. It is the sense of the Congress that sanctioning bodies and State boxing commissions should follow these ABC guidelines.May 26, 2000","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Appeals process","label":"b Appeals process","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide to the boxer a written explanation of the organization’s criteria, its rating of the boxer, and the rationale or basis for its rating (including a response to any specific questions submitted by the boxer); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submit a copy of its explanation to the Association of Boxing Commissions.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Notification of change in rating","label":"c Notification of change in rating","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"posts a copy, within 7 days of such change, on its Internet website or home page, if any, including an explanation of such change, for a period of not less than 30 days; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provides a copy of the rating change and explanation to an association to which at least a majority of the State boxing commissions belong.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Public disclosure","label":"d Public disclosure","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Federal Trade Commission filing","label":"1 Federal Trade Commission filing","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a complete description of the organization’s ratings criteria, policies, and general sanctioning fee schedule;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the bylaws of the organization;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the appeals procedure of the organization for a boxer’s rating; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F1%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a list and business address of the organization’s officials who vote on the ratings of boxers.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Format; updates","label":"2 Format; updates","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide the information required under paragraph (1) in writing, and, for any document greater than 2 pages in length, also in electronic form; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"promptly notify the Federal Trade Commission of any material change in the information submitted.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Federal Trade Commission to make information available to public","label":"3 Federal Trade Commission to make information available to public","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Federal Trade Commission shall make information received under this subsection available to the public. The Commission may assess sanctioning organizations a fee to offset the costs it incurs in processing the information and making it available to the public.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Internet alternative","label":"4 Internet alternative","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is readily accessible by the general public using generally available search engines and does not require a password or payment of a fee for full access to all the information;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"contains all the information required to be submitted to the Federal Trade Commission by paragraph (1) in an easy to search and use format; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s6307c/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs6307c%2Fd%2F4%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is updated whenever there is a material change in the information.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
